{"tid":2503942,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"90萬訂閱cheap精全港首席萬年油KOL 點cook guide馬田肯收皮未[3]","createTime":"2021-04-25T12:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T11:17:45.000Z","uid":57911,"like":27,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb61f6933514c51e41ca5fc9d277422a405bb22","tid":2503942,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">罪名一：唔願意面對賣注脂牛質疑</span></strong></span><br />\n平時啲片理論多多，啲人要佢解釋返點解啲肉會咁就唔理人<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaiBkE7urvPzgqzRrYLc3ppasXNtDuZNCGr4z97HT6iHc?filename=RJjsDuo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRJjsDuo.gif&h=fcd0eee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">罪名二：萬年油餵明星食</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT1G3SxBspFYvG3cePShjH3pXd3ZxaGNGzw6z5W4vx8ef?filename=L3y4AoS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3y4AoS.jpg&h=8c1a06d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019年5月嘅油<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeFLx6fCqCw94yWzu9Nu5VGzBu3oxeV3yskmqFb5HGmo7?filename=kkBUXCs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkkBUXCs.png&h=b84e5afb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2021年2月煮笑口棗餵俾鄭中基食<br />\n<br />\n如果對方事前唔知道的話係十分賤格冇品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">罪名三：怨婦tag</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n馬田面對賣中資廣告嘅回應<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSzsoq7g8rocLehQxKoLUzLiAFKwRFFiVGP3aS6UFtuKM?filename=Lg0sEMr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLg0sEMr.png&h=fa3dbab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbS9AKozJ1tKHN56BUzjTutPkvoReuomXRApXXWPh9mvH?filename=SiqXhye.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSiqXhye.jpg&h=fc1be407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaDDY48So93qdGu8qvi4fbDNiytQC88fWmKZoCY3ia8fF?filename=TPR3Xyi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTPR3Xyi.jpg&h=3a3c2603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牛旨被質疑賣注脂牛時嘅回應<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZtHd2jybfE7dGtyLewKdVf8Qjx8tUQQGZ9ZzQ4SuVFZx?filename=vpv4G0g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvpv4G0g.jpg&h=265a598c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPSZYcVwdWYdJSSRRVfmRvH5sAWUc1HFuZwvF8uVf9Vq1?filename=vcakfko.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvcakfko.jpg&h=3f2c12f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">罪名四：刪檔直播圍爐放狗咬人</span></strong></span><br />\n注脂牛事件、中資廣告事件、甚至佢自己爆料食觀眾事件<br />\n全部嘢都係人哋屈咗佢，佢好冤枉不過直播已經刪咗死冇對證<br />\n然後有真fans跟咗直播話件事唔係咁，不過冇人查得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A真係注脂牛？<br />\n<br />\n其實冇人知係唔係注脂牛，不過睇張圖就唔少人都質疑佢係注脂牛<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaiBkE7urvPzgqzRrYLc3ppasXNtDuZNCGr4z97HT6iHc?filename=RJjsDuo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRJjsDuo.gif&h=fcd0eee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而應該負責解釋嘅馬田就淨係以po頭嗰幾張圖回應件事<br />\n並冇正正經經咁解釋食物來源同埋圖中現象成因<br />\n亦冇交代清楚係唔係注脂牛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A之前幾個po好多專家都講到好似係好常出現嘅現像<br />\n<br />\n理論上應該係由馬田嚟答，佢平時啲煮食片都會講下啲原論，唔知點解今次用幾個tag就想打發人走<br />\n<br />\n如果你係真fans都可以代馬田拍驗證片(唔洗出樣)<br />\n材料用返唔同超級市場買到嘅凍肉<br />\n(最好有收據證明返邊舊肉喺邊間超級市場買)<br />\n然後拍片切返一粒粒再用返上面張爆漿圖嗰種方式煎<br />\n如果超級市場凍肉都出現同樣現象就代表理論成立<br />\n此po亦都會自動收皮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A點先會放過馬田<br />\n<br />\n馬田交代清楚疑似注脂牛嘅來源同現象<br />\n同埋後續會點樣跟進<br />\n例如換供應商<br />\n<br />\n或者馬田同牛旨劃清界線<br />\n同以後唔再賣牛旨廣告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身個po俾人移咗去娛樂台<br />\n基於食品安全嘅問題<br />\n決定第2個po轉過嚟飲食台開"},{"pid":"c44778e6e7be214a7a772bee2a6403f9a9a250ba","tid":2503942,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T12:58:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be5d13d1f6e7a4a00f1c05dc5e7fd9ddb1e6bede","tid":2503942,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T13:24:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39696362fb059f71c72d40e64d1bfd73aa222459","tid":2503942,"uid":81006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"點解會有咁多人訂閱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"3739c8f2cd53e2ea8744a0ad88e73f2ef30ded53","tid":2503942,"uid":61653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T13:27:09.000Z","msg":"唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要聲討人幫中資賣廣告問過佢地未<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRKXT3pe8CSemJHtjaRvqqxvqQeEoiGnwEDbWqmFDVuRr?filename=pQ3L4wB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQ3L4wB.jpg&h=4a4acf7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3ddc4f9cc417317eb0511dfab0df55765bc13f9","tid":2503942,"uid":57911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"39696362fb059f71c72d40e64d1bfd73aa222459","tid":2503942,"uid":81006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"點解會有咁多人訂閱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T13:28:15.000Z","msg":"佢同台灣個遊戲youtuber合作搞咗個搞神馬<br />\n所以多咗班台灣觀眾"},{"pid":"d94aed3baf8955e760bffb1f2eab699ad1794aaa","tid":2503942,"uid":57911,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3739c8f2cd53e2ea8744a0ad88e73f2ef30ded53","tid":2503942,"uid":61653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T13:27:09.000Z","msg":"唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/no